====================================

This pack is derived from:
    Schedule Assessment Guide: Best Practices for Project Schedules
    US Government Accountability Office (GAO), GAO-16-89G
    December 2015

Source licence: Public Domain (US Government work, 17 U.S.C. 105); GAO reproduction
